OL,3,C'A death sentence for shoplifting':
OL,4,CSaints 'in shock' over spygate
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,FSouthampton being expelled from the
OL,8,FChampionship play-off final is like
OL,9,Fbeing handed "a death sentence for
OL,10,Fshoplifting."
OL,12,FSenior reporter at the Southampton
OL,13,FDaily Echo, Alfie House says people at
OL,14,Fthe club have told him that they are
OL,15,Fin shock and believe their punishment
OL,16,Ffor the "spygate scandal" is the
OL,17,Fstrongest sporting sanction ever
OL,18,Fissued.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
