PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779286286
OL,3,C'A death sentence for shoplifting':
OL,4,CSaints 'in shock' over spygate
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,FOn Tuesday night the EFL confirmed
OL,8,Fthat Saints will not be able to take
OL,9,Fpart in the play-off final at Wembley
OL,10,Fon Saturday after "admitting multiple
OL,11,Fbreaches of EFL Regulations".
OL,13,FIt currently means the side's dreams
OL,14,Fof promotion to the Premier League are
OL,15,Fover, but the club are appealing the
OL,16,Fdecision.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian's sport
OL,19,Fcorrespondent Andrew Pate, Alfie House
OL,20,Fsaid there's "anger at every level'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779286286
OL,3,C'A death sentence for shoplifting':
OL,4,CSaints 'in shock' over spygate
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,F"The senior staff that I've spoken to,
OL,8,Fthey're angry about what's happened,"
OL,9,Fhe said.
OL,11,F"The ordinary working people, of which
OL,12,Fthere are hundreds that prop up a
OL,13,Ffootball club, they're angry as well.
OL,14,FI think the fans made their thoughts
OL,15,Fvery clear.
OL,17,F"It leaves the club in a difficult
OL,18,Fposition - they were playing for #200
OL,19,Fmillion on Saturday and now they're
OL,20,Fnot, as it stands."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
