PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779286286
OL,3,C'A death sentence for shoplifting':
OL,4,CSaints 'in shock' over spygate
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,FThe 'spygate' scandal all started when
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough reported to the EFL that
OL,9,Fa member of Southampton staff had
OL,10,Fspied on a training session on May 7,
OL,11,Fin breach of league rules, with the
OL,12,FEFL charging them the following day.
OL,14,FBut Southampton FC were also found to
OL,15,Fhave spied on Oxford United in
OL,16,FDecember 2025 and Ipswich Town in
OL,17,FApril 2026.
OL,19,FMr House added that there are now two
OL,20,F"totally different financial
OL,21,Fforecasts".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779286286
OL,3,C'A death sentence for shoplifting':
OL,4,CSaints 'in shock' over spygate
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,F"Players are going to be sold this
OL,8,Fsummer, the squad's going to need a
OL,9,Flot of work done and I think staff are
OL,10,Fprobably going to leave off the back
OL,11,Fof this," he added.
OL,13,F"It changes everything.
OL,15,F"The appeal is not about whether
OL,16,Fthey've been guilty or not - the
OL,17,Fclub's admitted they've done this on
OL,18,Fthree occasions.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779286286
OL,3,C'A death sentence for shoplifting':
OL,4,CSaints 'in shock' over spygate
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,F"It's the worst spying operation ever
OL,8,Fbecause they didn't win any of those
OL,9,Fthree games."
OL,11,FA decision on Southampton's appeal is
OL,12,Fexpected from the appeal panel by the
OL,13,Fend of today, but Alfie adds if their
OL,14,Fappeal is rejected - it will have "a
OL,15,Fmassive impact."
OL,17,F"Already this morning there's been
OL,18,Fmedia reports about players like
OL,19,FCaspar Jander potentially leaving the
OL,20,Fclub this summer, and I think we're
OL,21,Fgoing to see that all summer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779286286
OL,3,C'A death sentence for shoplifting':
OL,4,CSaints 'in shock' over spygate
OL,5,Cpunishment
OL,7,F"I think there will be some staff that
OL,8,Fleave the club as a result of this,
OL,9,Fwhether that's by choice or by force."
OL,11,FThe EFL has confirmed the game at
OL,12,FWembley will go ahead regardless of
OL,13,Fwhether Southampton's appeal is
OL,14,Fsuccessful or not.
OL,16,FShould the tie remain between
OL,17,FMiddlesbrough and Hull, the game will
OL,18,Fkick off at 3.30pm but this will be at
OL,19,Fthe later time of 4.30pm should
OL,20,FSouthampton be reinstated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
